-- Danone Plans $696 Million Share Buyback After Stake Sales; Confirms Goals
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-21T05:29:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/danone-plans-696-million-share-buyback-wit-stake-proceeds-confirms-goals.html
Groupe Danone SA confirmed its
targets for 2010 and said it plans a 500 million-euro share
buyback with the proceeds from the sale of stakes in businesses
in Russia and China.  Third-quarter sales rose to 4.347 billion euros from 3.780
billion euros a year earlier, the company said in an emailed
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
